ziegfeld girl is a 1941 american romantic comedy film directed by robert z. leonard and written by robert z. leonard . the film stars william powell , hedy lamarr , adele mara , douglass dumbrille and lana turner . the film stars william powell , hedy lamarr , adele mara , douglass dumbrille , adele mara , douglass dumbrille , lucien littlefield , and james stewart . the film was released by warner bros. on december 14 , 1941 , by metro-goldwyn-mayer .